        "text": "<p><strong>The Qure Faucet Filter</strong> is designed to remove harmful impurities from your water, ensuring your skin remains clear, hydrated, and free from irritants.</p><p>This guide will walk you through the installation process so you can start enjoying cleaner, skin-friendly water in just a few minutes.</p>"
